# ATLAS Interceptors Directory

This directory contains HTTP interceptors for ATLAS API requests.

Interceptors to be implemented:
- atlas-auth.interceptor.ts - Automatically attaches authentication tokens and headers
  - Adds JWT Bearer token or API key
  - Adds ATLAS-specific headers (API version, client ID)
  - Handles 401 Unauthorized with token refresh and retry
  - Handles 403 Forbidden with appropriate error messages
  - Enforces HTTPS for all ATLAS API communications
  - Logs all requests and responses for debugging

Interceptors are registered in the ATLAS module providers.
